pull_request.title: change sphincs variant enablement
pull_request.body:
Changes the default enablement settings for some Sphincs+ algorithms to activate variants [favoured by NIST](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/blob/cf6d8a059e446d24e2af06949d83605ae0f4f414/.CMake/alg_support.cmake#L542).

- [x] documentation is added or updated
- [na] tests are added or updated

Enables profiling of NIST-standardized sig algs as per https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/pull/86

pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `12ad5be` to `cf6d8a0`.
Commits
  • cf6d8a0 adding OpenSSL3 test; activating sanitizer test (#1363)
  • f214011 Fixed mismatch between YAML and markdown docs for some algorithms. (#1365)

  • 924ea88 Updated PQClean commit in copy_from_upstream.yml (#1359)
  • 1d76b2e add cpack (for .deb packages) (#1362)
  • da0dd47 Config update (#1361)
  • fe3cb02 NIST std algs list selection enablement (#1355)
  • aed3b49 Build Doxygen docs in whatever the CMake build directory is (#1357)
  • f272232 Build dump_alg_info in tests (#1353)
  • f30cae9 Fix Doxygen Markdown failures (#1349)
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
